sequenceDiagram
    participant Browser
    participant Web as apps/web
    participant Manager
    participant CAS as Institutional CAS server
    participant Redis

    rect rgb(230, 240, 255)
    Note over Browser,CAS: Flow A - CAS SSO (students)
    Browser->>Web: click "Login with CAS"
    Web->>Manager: full page redirect GET /api/auth/cas
    Manager->>CAS: redirect to CAS login (service=BASE_URL/api/auth/cas)
    CAS->>Browser: institutional login page
    Browser->>CAS: submit credentials
    CAS->>Manager: redirect back with service ticket
    Manager->>CAS: serviceValidate (XML) ticket check
    CAS-->>Manager: XML attributes (NRP, Jurusan, name, ...)
    alt first login
        Manager->>Manager: parse NRP -> year/degreeLevel, match Jurusan -> study_program
        Manager->>Manager: auto-provision user + student row
    end
    Manager->>Redis: create session (session:rest / session:data)
    Manager->>Browser: Set-Cookie session=...; redirect to / with toast cookie
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 230)
    Note over Browser,Manager: Flow B - Password login (instructor/admin)
    Browser->>Web: submit email/password on /login
    Web->>Manager: POST /api/auth/login
    Manager->>Manager: Bun.password.verify(password, user.passwordHash)
    Manager->>Redis: create session
    Manager-->>Web: 200 OK, Set-Cookie session=...
    Web->>Manager: GET /api/auth/me (refresh)
    Manager-->>Web: user + role profile
    Web->>Web: useAuthStore.user = data, navigate to /
    end

    rect rgb(235, 255, 235)
    Note over Browser,Manager: Every subsequent request
    Browser->>Manager: HTTP request with session cookie
    Manager->>Redis: sessions.get(cookieValue) -> user id -> Session data
    Redis-->>Manager: {id, role}
    Manager->>Manager: auth/protected/private(roles) macros authorize
    Manager->>Redis: extend TTL (sliding expiry, SESSION_TTL=3h)

    Browser->>Manager: WebSocket connect, auth={session: cookie}
    Manager->>Redis: sessions.get(session) (same store as HTTP)
    Manager-->>Browser: connection accepted, socket.data.session set
    end
